    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for Morrison COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed under the Minimal profile. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been addressed: 7 were formally assessed and 6 were documented as epistemic gaps with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. The package is accepted for submission as a complete Minimal-profile evidence record. The identified credibility gaps are acknowledged and documented; regulatory disposition of the underlying model remains not accepted pending resolution of the factor deficiencies.",
